---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 mt-auto">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- 關於計畫 -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">WZULTC 跨語照護</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
          文藻跨語照護計畫致力於提供越南移工優質的華語教學與文化適應支援，促進跨文化理解與社會共融。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- 快速連結 -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">快速連結</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors">計畫說明</a></li>
          <li><a href="/team" class="hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors">主持團隊</a></li>
          <li><a href="/course" class="hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors">華語教材</a></li>
          <li><a href="/enroll" class="hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors">招募資訊</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors">聯絡我們</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 聯絡資訊 -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">聯絡資訊</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <span>wzultc@gmail.com</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>台灣</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-700 mt-8 pt-8 text-center text-sm">
      <p>&copy; {currentYear} WZULTC. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400">
        Built with <a href="https://astro.build" class="hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
